This project highlights the research and collaboration activities within the Group of Artificial Intelligence in Agriculture (GAIA) at Texas A&M AgriLife Research.

The lab focuses on developing AI-driven solutions for precision agriculture, including computer vision, machine learning, and geospatial analytics.

